@* Inline notice rendered into the right-hand detail panel when the requested
   issue doesn't exist or the viewer can't see it. Wording is generic so the
   GUID doesn't get confirmed-or-denied. *@
<div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center h-100 text-muted">
    <div class="text-center p-4">
        <i class="fa-regular fa-circle-question fa-2x mb-2 d-block"></i>
        <p class="mb-0">@Localizer["Issue_Unavailable"]</p>
    </div>
</div>
